summary: Imagine Jason getting asked about you during an interview. Reporter: “So Jason! When you met, was it love at first sight?”...
caption:
Imagine Jason getting asked about you during an interview.

Reporter: “So Jason! When you met, was it love at first sight?”

Jason: “For me yes. For her… It was another story.” Said Jason with a smiling face.

Reporter: “Explain to us! Everybody wants to know!”

Jason: “We met in a jazz club and… I literally spilled my Guinness on her dress…”

Reporter: “No way!”

Jason: “I swear… But then… Look where we are today! A wedding, two wonderful kids and many plans for the future. I cannot thank enough my clumsiness!” Jason answered, laughing out loud.
